---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout locale="en" title="For Closers & Appointment Setters — ClosersMatch" description="Join the ClosersMatch network. Certified training, vetted companies, and assignments that fit you. You close. We handle the rest.">

  <!-- ================================================
       HERO
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="vc-hero">
    <div class="container vc-hero__inner">
      <div class="vc-hero__content">
        <span class="label label--red">For closers &amp; appointment setters</span>
        <h1 class="vc-hero__title">
          You close deals.<br />
          <span class="vc-hero__title-red">We handle<br />the rest.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="vc-hero__subtitle">
          ClosersMatch is not a job board. It is a performance-driven ecosystem for ambitious sales professionals. Certified training, vetted companies, and assignments that truly fit you.
        </p>
        <div class="vc-hero__trust-pills">
          <span class="trust-pill">✓ CM Certified training</span>
          <span class="trust-pill">✓ Vetted companies</span>
          <span class="trust-pill">✓ Tailored matching</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-hero__actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--lg">Apply as a closer →</a>
          <a href="#hoe-het-werkt" class="btn btn--outline-dark-mode">How it works</a>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-hero__note">Only approved members get access.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vc-hero__visual">
        <div class="vc-hero__process-card">
          <div class="vc-process-step vc-process-step--active">
            <div class="vc-process-step__num">01</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Screening</strong>
              <span>You apply and we review your profile</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vc-process-step__badge vc-process-step__badge--done">✓</div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-process-step">
            <div class="vc-process-step__num">02</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Training</strong>
              <span>CM Certified training and real-world scenarios</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vc-process-step__badge">→</div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-process-step">
            <div class="vc-process-step__num">03</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Matching</strong>
              <span>Matched with companies that fit you</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vc-process-step__badge">→</div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-process-step">
            <div class="vc-process-step__num">04</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Grow</strong>
              <span>Close deals, keep learning, and earn</span>
            </div>
            <div class="vc-process-step__badge">→</div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-hero__card-footer">
            <span>50+ successful matches</span>
            <span class="vc-hero__card-dot">•</span>
            <span>CM Certified network</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       WAAROM CLOSERSMATCH
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vc-waarom">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vc-waarom__inner">
        <div class="vc-waarom__content">
          <span class="label">Why ClosersMatch</span>
          <h2 class="h2 vc-waarom__title">Top salespeople do not lack<br />talent. They lack<br /><span class="vc-waarom__title-red">access.</span></h2>
          <p class="vc-waarom__body">Top performers stall not because they lack skill, but because they lack the right environment. No quality leads. No fair commission structures. No coaching that actually helps. ClosersMatch fixes that.</p>
          <p class="vc-waarom__body">We give you access to companies that are ready, training that makes you genuinely better, and a system that makes your results visible. So you earn more. Every month.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-waarom__blocks">
          <div class="vc-waarom__block">
            <div class="vc-waarom__block-icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="vc-waarom__block-title">Better companies</h3>
              <p class="vc-waarom__block-text">Only vetted companies with proven offers, fair commission, and warm leads. No cold calling. No uncertain months.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-waarom__block">
            <div class="vc-waarom__block-icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="vc-waarom__block-title">Real coaching</h3>
              <p class="vc-waarom__block-text">Conversation analysis, call reviews, and direct feedback after every call. You get better whether you like it or not.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-waarom__block">
            <div class="vc-waarom__block-icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="vc-waarom__block-title">Insight into your performance</h3>
              <p class="vc-waarom__block-text">You see what you close, what you miss, and what to improve next week. No guesswork. Just data.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-waarom__block">
            <div class="vc-waarom__block-icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="vc-waarom__block-title">Community of top performers</h3>
              <p class="vc-waarom__block-text">You do not work alone. You work inside a network of certified closers and setters who keep each other sharp.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       TWEE ROLLEN
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vc-rollen">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vc-rollen__header">
        <span class="label">Choose your entry role</span>
        <h2 class="h2 vc-rollen__title">Two roles. One ecosystem.<br />You choose where you start.</h2>
        <p class="vc-rollen__sub">Whether you already have experience or are just starting out, there is a place for you at ClosersMatch.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vc-rollen__grid">

        <div class="vc-rol-card vc-rol-card--setter">
          <div class="vc-rol-card__header">
            <span class="vc-rol-card__overline">Beginners welcome</span>
            <h3 class="vc-rol-card__title">Appointment Setter</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="vc-rol-card__body">You learn how to qualify leads, open conversations, and keep prospects warm. Real hands-on experience with real companies, every day. When you are ready, the step up to closer is a natural next move.</p>
          <ul class="vc-rol-card__list">
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              No years of sales experience required
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Paid per qualified appointment
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              CM Setter training included
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Clear path to closer available
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--outline-red vc-rol-card__cta">Start as an appointment setter →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-rol-card vc-rol-card--closer">
          <div class="vc-rol-card__badge">Most popular</div>
          <div class="vc-rol-card__header">
            <span class="vc-rol-card__overline">For experienced sales professionals</span>
            <h3 class="vc-rol-card__title">Closer</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="vc-rol-card__body">You run the conversations, uncover needs, and close the deal. At ClosersMatch, closers are matched to companies where your approach works, and where warm leads are already waiting. No cold outreach.</p>
          <ul class="vc-rol-card__list">
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Warm leads, no cold calling
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Paid per closed deal
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              CM Certified badge for your profile
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Matched by industry and deal size
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--red vc-rol-card__cta">Become a CM Certified closer →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       HOE HET WERKT
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vc-hiw" id="hoe-het-werkt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vc-hiw__header">
        <span class="label">The process</span>
        <h2 class="h2 vc-hiw__title">From application to<br />your first deal.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="vc-hiw__steps">

        <div class="vc-hiw__step">
          <div class="vc-hiw__step-left">
            <div class="vc-hiw__step-num">01</div>
            <div class="vc-hiw__step-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-hiw__step-content">
            <h3 class="vc-hiw__step-title">Apply &amp; screening</h3>
            <p class="vc-hiw__step-text">You apply through the form. We review your background, motivation, and potential. Only suitable candidates move forward. That is how we keep network quality high.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-hiw__step">
          <div class="vc-hiw__step-left">
            <div class="vc-hiw__step-num">02</div>
            <div class="vc-hiw__step-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-hiw__step-content">
            <h3 class="vc-hiw__step-title">CM Certified training</h3>
            <p class="vc-hiw__step-text">Not a certificate for the wall. You learn how to steer every conversation, handle objections, and close the deal, including the tough ones. Intensive role-play, real scenarios, direct feedback.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-hiw__step">
          <div class="vc-hiw__step-left">
            <div class="vc-hiw__step-num">03</div>
            <div class="vc-hiw__step-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-hiw__step-content">
            <h3 class="vc-hiw__step-title">Matching with a company</h3>
            <p class="vc-hiw__step-text">We connect you with a company that fits your industry, sales style, and deal size. You get clarity on the product, the customer, and the sales process before you start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-hiw__step vc-hiw__step--last">
          <div class="vc-hiw__step-left">
            <div class="vc-hiw__step-num">04</div>
          </div>
          <div class="vc-hiw__step-content">
            <h3 class="vc-hiw__step-title">Close, learn &amp; grow</h3>
            <p class="vc-hiw__step-text">You get to work. Conversations are analyzed, feedback is given, and your results are tracked. Every week you get better. Every month you earn more.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="vc-hiw__cta">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--lg">Apply now →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       WAT JE KRIJGT
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vc-ecosystem">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vc-ecosystem__header">
        <span class="label label--red">The CM ecosystem</span>
        <h2 class="h2 vc-ecosystem__title">More than opportunities.<br />A complete system to grow.</h2>
        <p class="vc-ecosystem__sub">Everything you need to perform, improve, and earn, in one place.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vc-ecosystem__grid">

        <div class="vc-eco-card">
          <div class="vc-eco-card__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="vc-eco-card__title">Qualified assignments</h3>
          <p class="vc-eco-card__text">High-ticket companies with proven products, fair commission structures, and warm leads ready to be closed.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-eco-card">
          <div class="vc-eco-card__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="vc-eco-card__title">CM Certified training</h3>
          <p class="vc-eco-card__text">Intensive sales training built on real conversations. Role-play, scenarios, and direct feedback from experienced coaches.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-eco-card">
          <div class="vc-eco-card__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="vc-eco-card__title">Conversation analysis &amp; coaching</h3>
          <p class="vc-eco-card__text">Every conversation is analyzed. Conversion rates, objections, timing, you see exactly what can improve and how.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-eco-card">
          <div class="vc-eco-card__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="vc-eco-card__title">Ongoing guidance</h3>
          <p class="vc-eco-card__text">Not a one-off training and then you are on your own. Weekly coaching, reviews, and optimization for as long as you are active.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-eco-card">
          <div class="vc-eco-card__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="vc-eco-card__title">Performance dashboard</h3>
          <p class="vc-eco-card__text">See your pipeline, conversions, and earnings in real time. No surprises. Full control over your own performance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-eco-card">
          <div class="vc-eco-card__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="vc-eco-card__title">Network of top performers</h3>
          <p class="vc-eco-card__text">You become part of a community of certified closers and setters. Share knowledge. Stay sharp. Grow together.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       AI PERFORMANCE PLATFORM
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vc-ai">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vc-ai__inner">
        <div class="vc-ai__content">
          <span class="label label--red">AI Performance Platform</span>
          <h2 class="h2 vc-ai__title">See exactly why a deal<br />does or doesn't close.</h2>
          <p class="vc-ai__body">On top of the CM Certified training, you get access to the AI Performance Platform: your personal coach based on your own conversations. Practice first with AI across different scenarios and objections. When you then take the real call, by phone or online meeting, you get live feedback during the conversation and an in-depth analysis afterwards.</p>
          <ul class="vc-ai__list">
            <li>✓ Insight into discovery, authority checks, timing &amp; closing technique</li>
            <li>✓ Personal scoreboard with conversion rate per call</li>
            <li>✓ 3 live 1-on-1 coaching sessions with Stefan Kelderman</li>
            <li>✓ Verified Professional status, visible to clients</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/academy" class="btn btn--red vc-ai__cta">Discover the Academy &amp; AI platform →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-ai__visual">
          <div class="vc-ai__card">
            <div class="vc-ai__card-row"><span>Live feedback during calls</span><strong>✓</strong></div>
            <div class="vc-ai__card-row"><span>Analysis afterwards</span><strong>✓</strong></div>
            <div class="vc-ai__card-row"><span>Personal scoreboard</span><strong>✓</strong></div>
            <div class="vc-ai__card-row"><span>1-on-1 coaching with Stefan Kelderman</span><strong>✓</strong></div>
            <div class="vc-ai__card-row"><span>Verified profile</span><strong>✓</strong></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       TESTIMONIALS / SOCIAL PROOF
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vc-social">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vc-social__header">
        <span class="label">What members say</span>
        <h2 class="h2 vc-social__title">People already closing<br />for ClosersMatch.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="vc-social__grid">

        <div class="vc-quote-card">
          <div class="vc-quote-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="vc-quote-card__text">"I was stuck on platforms where I had to find my own leads. At ClosersMatch I got warm appointments right away and a company that was genuinely serious. €4,200 in commission in my first month."</p>
          <div class="vc-quote-card__author">
            <div class="vc-quote-card__avatar">JV</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Jeffrey V.</strong>
              <span>CM Certified Closer</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-quote-card vc-quote-card--featured">
          <div class="vc-quote-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="vc-quote-card__text">"I had zero sales experience. Through the setter route I learned how to qualify leads and open conversations. After three months I became a closer. Now I close deals for an energy company."</p>
          <div class="vc-quote-card__author">
            <div class="vc-quote-card__avatar">MG</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Malu G.</strong>
              <span>CM Certified Closer, started as setter</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vc-quote-card">
          <div class="vc-quote-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="vc-quote-card__text">"The training is not soft. You get feedback that cuts. But my conversion rate went from 22% to 58% in six weeks. That speaks for itself."</p>
          <div class="vc-quote-card__author">
            <div class="vc-quote-card__avatar">RV</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Robert V.</strong>
              <span>CM Certified Closer</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="vc-social__stats">
        <div class="vc-social__stat">
          <span class="vc-social__stat-num">50+</span>
          <span class="vc-social__stat-label">Successful matches</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-social__stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="vc-social__stat">
          <span class="vc-social__stat-num">CM</span>
          <span class="vc-social__stat-label">Certified badge, recognized mark of quality</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-social__stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="vc-social__stat">
          <span class="vc-social__stat-num">48u</span>
          <span class="vc-social__stat-label">Average time to first match</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       AFSLUITENDE CTA
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="vc-closing">
    <div class="vc-closing__inner">
      <span class="label label--ghost-light">Limited spots available</span>
      <h2 class="vc-closing__title">
        Ready to earn serious<br />money in sales?
      </h2>
      <p class="vc-closing__body">
        ClosersMatch is not a platform for people who want to try sales.<br />
        It is an ecosystem for people who want to excel.<br /><br />
        Apply. Get screened. Close deals. Grow.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--xl vc-closing__btn">Apply as a closer →</a>
      <p class="vc-closing__sub">Free to apply. No obligations. Motivated sales professionals only.</p>
      <p class="vc-closing__brand">ClosersMatch. <span>The Revenue Ecosystem.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ====================================================
     HERO
  ==================================================== */
  .vc-hero {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 162px 0 80px;
  }

  .vc-hero__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .vc-hero__content .label--red {
    background: rgba(221,52,46,0.1);
    color: var(--color-red);
    border: 1px solid rgba(221,52,46,0.25);
  }

  .vc-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.8vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-black);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 20px 0 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .vc-hero__title-red { color: var(--color-red); }

  .vc-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #4B5563;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .vc-hero__trust-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .trust-pill {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-black);
    background: var(--color-gray-light);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .vc-hero__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
